{"tid":1242072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【公投中】各位會唔會支持林鄭月娥未來三年繼續施政呢﹖","createTime":"2019-06-19T02:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T05:39:45.000Z","uid":16628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b6181de4c3e61eef8ca9d2dcd9f9c9c272dbfd59","tid":1242072,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:33:40.000Z","msg":"<ins>借朋友account開post</ins><br />\n<br />\n各位連登巴打絲打，第一次出post，想大家幫手去呢個Facebook Page 投個反對票！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/263384634045118/posts/818500458533530?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F263384634045118%2Fposts%2F818500458533530%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=7f1fb117\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/263384634045118/posts/818500458533530?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQLhmLb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQLhmLb.png&h=a3b1cb37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有冇感覺過無助嘅感覺。呢兩星期嘅反送中事件如預期跌watt，就如以往香港好多人都只係三分鐘熱度。<br />\n<br />\n我明200萬人上街好震撼，好多靚相，好多所謂「感動位」。但當初點解行出黎，我諗唔係要搏呢啲打飛機位。係因為大家覺得星期日上街「可以做，應該做，亦願意做。」<br />\n<br />\n人在江湖，工要繼續返。我問自己呢個白領呀叔可以做啲乜：除左繼續有得上街就上，有集會就去，得閒/食飯時都會追擊個啲所謂愛港愛國post。<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇用架，但希望個啲浮游藍絲可以睇清楚啲真藍絲有幾無人性，無良知，無邏輯。同埋反抗背後有資金支持嘅造勢facebook page。<br />\n<br />\n「如果連登係一個總部，其中一類戰場就係出面，係呢啲不知所謂嘅facebook page到入面」。<br />\n<br />\n上面個投票就黎完，而家有72%嘅人支持林鄭。支持定反對都好，希望大家去投個票。你嘅每一個動作都好重要！<br />\n<br />\n除左呢個post，亦呼籲大家運用連登智慧，港式幽默，人類良知去追擊呢啲專頁 / post。"},{"pid":"e54ecd05b0446d095768d2ff6bde1eabd2552c08","tid":1242072,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:47:29.000Z","msg":"咁多垃圾5毛page <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bbf109efc84fc0245c6e417f4b565ebaa2b99f","tid":1242072,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:26:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7844929758521971f5232d48c8da9900c523d6c7","tid":1242072,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f188ce0fee64706eaa03fe76b8375846014b1eca","tid":1242072,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:34:36.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"6f3c11c5f3c87378915720ea3e98c6986d938659","tid":1242072,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:34:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6169f3002bae53168750a9e05584ad1e65ec132f","tid":1242072,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:36:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec400d4fcdc318acfd2fc412fcf49a90c7271960","tid":1242072,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:47:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4c8f78e18761d8147fd848c1767e3c351e436a4","tid":1242072,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd947627a18ae8ba12de275e4b524eaed64a7914","tid":1242072,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:47:57.000Z","msg":"Help"},{"pid":"4ed8f963dc743413aa7dc4110023569e0c2781a4","tid":1242072,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:49:24.000Z","msg":"得番4個鐘咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7id3h51.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7id3h51.png&h=1a736a94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20fbacc7942e87bc5f78121ad6aafd3d72507074","tid":1242072,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:49:36.000Z","msg":"好嬲啊"},{"pid":"3517e52d734cc5e0e443ed9fdf14875c6d474fce","tid":1242072,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8009e64ca9cd2fa5ec9a8b123e62ed7bc2fd531","tid":1242072,"uid":16628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:39:45.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}